commit.description:
Add ConsistencyCollector for simulator cross-run checking

ConsistencyCollector<T> records outputs from multiple simulator runs
and checks for coordination inconsistencies:

- check_prefix_consistency(): all runs must produce prefixes of the
  same sequence (for Seq/TotalOrder sinks)
- check_set_consistency(): all runs must produce the same set of
  elements (for Conv/SetInclusion sinks)

Usage with exhaustive mode:
  let collector = ConsistencyCollector::new();
  sim.exhaustive(async || {
      let outputs = out_recv.collect_sorted().await;
      collector.record_run(outputs);
  });
  collector.check_prefix_consistency();
